content.txt1: Tama taama nummaak numtin amoh taama celta taama abtam duddah, takkay immay lowsis gubat haanam, apps, w.w.w., ku telfoonul, kee kaadu inki inki meklah applicationitte faktam duddah. Akah kinnim, lowsis taama, mekla abaanam, w.w.w., nanu maqar luk sugneeh, atu dubuk elle faxximta innal, script addat tan ximmooma inkih edde raddam faxximta.
content.txt2: Ta taamah addat mannal alfimtam: Ta applicationik buxah galih addat, buxah addah galih addal auliyary functionitte elle faxximta innal, hinnay "inkih yan taama kee exit" button buxah addah galil. Tama adranto inkih tan abtootah alfimam kee tama appil aliftam cayla.
content.txt3: Nanu ta tuxxiq edde nantifiqem ni assabalta gersi assabaltooti faktam kee ken lowsis, axcih intagram, toh sissikuk slide abak video digirik lakal, kee farmo ruuban farmo saanih kataysis, w.
